\c 24
\p
\v 1 Pamazuva ake Nebhukadhinezari mambo weBhabhironi wakakwira\x + 2 Makor. 36.6. Dhan. 1.1.\x*; Jehoyakimu ndokuva muranda wake makore matatu; ndokudzoka ndokumupandukira\x + Jer. 25.1.\x*.
\v 2 Jehovha wakatuma kwaari\x + Jer. 25.9. 32.28. Eze. 19.8.\x* hondo dzakarongwa dzeVaKaradhiya\x + 25.4. Jer. 35.11.\x*, nehondo dzakarongwa dzeVaSiriya\x + 6.23.\x*\x + 25.4. Jer. 35.11.\x*, nehondo dzakarongwa dzevaMoabhu\x + 6.23.\x*\x + 13.20.\x*, nehondo dzakarongwa dzevana vaAmoni\x + 1 Sam. 11.1.\x*, ndokudzituma kurwisa Judha kuriparadza, zvichienderana neshoko raJehovha raakataura neruoko rwevaranda vake vaporofita\x + 20.17. 21,12,13,14. 23.27.\x*.
\v 3 Zvirokwazvo nemurairo waJehovha \add izvi\add* zvawira Judha, ku\add va\add*bvisa kubva pachiso chake, nekuda kwezvivi zvaManase\x + 21.11.\x*, zvichienderana nezvose zvaakaita;
\v 4 uyewo \add nekuda kwe\add*ropa risina mhosva raakateura; nokuti wakazadza Jerusarema neropa risina mhosva; Jehovha akasada kukanganwira\x + 21.16.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Zvino dzimwe dzenyaya dzaJehoyakimu, nezvose zvaakaita, hazvina kunyorwa here mubhuku reMakoronike emadzimambo aJudha?
\v 6 Jehoyakimu ndokurara nemadzibaba ake; mwanakomana wake Jehoyakini ndokuva mambo pachinzvimbo chake.
\v 7 Zvino mambo weEgipita haana kudzokororazve kubuda munyika yake, nokuti mambo weBhabhironi waiva atora kubva parukova rweEgipita kusvika parwizi Furati zvose zvaiva zvamambo weEgipita.
\p
\v 8 Jehoyakini waiva nemakore gumi nemasere paakava mambo, ndokutonga paJerusarema mwedzi mitatu. Uye zita ramai vake raiva Nehushuta mukunda waErinatani weJerusarema\x + 2 Makor. 36.9.\x*.
\v 9 Zvino wakaita chakaipa pameso paJehovha, zvichienderana nezvose madzibaba ake zvaakaita\x + 24.19. 23.37.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Panguva iyo varanda vaNebhukadhinezari mambo weBhabhironi vakakwira kuJerusarema; guta ndokupinda pakukombwa.
\v 11 Nebhukadhinezari mambo weBhabhironi ndokusvika kurwisa guta, varanda vake vakarikomba.
\v 12 Zvino Jehoyakini mambo waJudha wakabudira kuna mambo weBhabhironi\x + Jer. 24.1. 29.1,2. Eze. 17.12. 2 Makor. 36.10.\x*, iye namai vake, nevaranda vake, nemachinda ake, nevatenwa vake; mambo weBhabhironi ndokumutora mugore rerusere rekutonga kwake.
\v 13 Zvino wakabudisapo nefuma yose yeimba yaJehovha, nefuma yeimba yamambo\x + 20.17.\x*, ndokutema-tema nhumbi dzose dzegoridhe\x + 16.17. 2 Makor. 36.7. Ezi. 1.7. Dhan. 1.2. 5.2,3.\x* Soromoni mambo waIsraeri dzaaiva aita mutembere yaJehovha\x + 1 Madz. 7.48-50.\x*, Jehovha sezvaaiva areva\x + Jer. 20.5.\x*.
\v 14 Zvino wakatapa Jerusarema rese, nemachinda ese, nevane simba vemhare vose\x + Jer. 24.1.\x*, vatapwa vane zvuru gumi\x + 24.16. Jer. 52.28.\x*, nemhizha dzese, nevapfuri\x + 24.16. Jer. 24.1. 29.2. 1 Sam. 13.19,22.\x*; hakuna wakasiiwa kunze kwevepasi vevanhu venyika\x + 25.12.\x*.
\v 15 Zvino wakatapira Jehoyakini kuBhabhironi\x + 2 Makor. 36.10. Esi. 2.6. Eze. 1.2.\x*, namai vamambo, nevakadzi vamambo, nevatenwa vake, nevane simba venyika, akavatapira kuBhabhironi vachibva paJerusarema\x + Eki. 15.15. Eze. 17.13. 32.21.\x*.
\v 16 Zvino varume vose vesimba\x + 24.14. 15.20.\x*, zvuru zvinomwe, nemhizha nevapfuri churu, ava vose vakasimba vaiita hondo; mambo weBhabhironi ndokuvauisa vari vatapwa kuBhabhironi\x + 24.16. Jer. 52.28.\x*.
\p
\v 17 Mambo weBhabhironi\x + Jer. 37.1.\x* ndokuita Mataniya babamunini vake mambo pachinzvimbo chake\x + 1 Makor. 3.15. 2 Makor. 36.10.\x*, ndokushandura zita rake kuva Zedhekia\x + 23.34.\x*.
\s Zedhekia mambo wekupedzisira waJudha
\p
\v 18 Zedhekia waiva nemakore makumi maviri nerimwe paakava mambo; ndokutonga paJerusarema makore gumi nerimwe\x + 25.21. Jer. 52.1-27.\x*. Uye zita ramai vake raiva Hamitari mukunda waJeremiya weRibhina\x + 23.31.\x*.
\v 19 Zvino wakaita chakaipa pameso paJehovha zvichienderana nezvose Jehoyakini zvaakaita\x + 23.37. 2 Makor. 36.12.\x*.
\v 20 Nokuti nekuda kwekutsamwa kwaJehovha izvi zvakaitika paJerusarema nekwaJudha kusvika avarasa kubva pamberi pake. Zedhekia ndokumukira mambo weBhabhironi\x + 2 Makor. 36.13. Jer. 27.11. Eze. 17.15. Jer. 37.7,8.\x*.
